          <h2 class="node-title"><a href="b/vietnam-first-and-last-impressions-scams-and-corruption.html">Vietnam First and Last Impressions: Scams and Corruption</a></h2>
    
          <div class="meta">Submitted by tomo on June 25, 2011 - 11:48pm</div>
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_7 first"><a href="category/type/vietnam.html" rel="tag" title="">Vietnam</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_119"><a href="category/tags/airport.html" rel="tag" title="">airport</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_115"><a href="category/tags/bribes.html" rel="tag" title="">bribes</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_117"><a href="category/tags/corruption.html" rel="tag" title="">corruption</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_116"><a href="category/tags/scams.html" rel="tag" title="">scams</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_118"><a href="category/tags/taxi.html" rel="tag" title="">taxi</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_120"><a href="category/tags/transvestite-prostitutes.html" rel="tag" title="">transvestite prostitutes</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_36 last"><a href="category/tags/travel.html" rel="tag" title="">travel</a></li>
</ul></div>
    
  </div> <!-- /.node-header -->

  <div class="content">
    
    <p>What&#39;s the first thing tourists to Vietnam do after deplaning? &nbsp;They go through immigration and then get in a taxi to go to their hotel, reverse on the way home.</p><p>Generally, people from Europe or the Americas need to pre-arrange a visa to enter Vietnam, unlike most other Asian countries, or they can be brave and pre-arrange a visa-on-arrival. &nbsp;</p><p>If you&#39;ve never gone this route, it works like this.</p>
<a href="b/vietnam-first-and-last-impressions-scams-and-corruption.html">Read the rest of this article...</a>  </div>

  <div class="links-wrapper">
    <ul class="links inline"><li class="blog_usernames_blog first"><a href="blogs/tomo.html" title="Read tomo&#039;s latest blog entries.">tomo&#039;s blog</a></li>
<li class="comment_comments"><a href="b/vietnam-first-and-last-impressions-scams-and-corruption.html#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">17 comments</a></li>
<li class="node_read_more"><a href="b/vietnam-first-and-last-impressions-scams-and-corruption.html" title="Read the rest of Vietnam First and Last Impressions: Scams and Corruption.">Read more</a></li>
<li class="disqus_comments last"><span><a href="b/vietnam-first-and-last-impressions-scams-and-corruption.html#disqus_thread" class="comments disqus-comments" title="Jump to the comments of this posting." data-disqus-identifier="node/197">Comments</a></span></li>
